import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent implements OnInit { users:any; constructor(private http:HttpClient){} ngOnInit(): void { this.http.get('http://localhost:5019/api/users').subscribe({ next:response=>this.users=response, error:error=>console.log(error) }) } title = 'Client'; }
